{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"There are a lot of ways\nthe people around us"},{"time":4308,"text":"can help improve our lives."},{"time":6435,"text":"We don't bump into every neighbor,"},{"time":8079,"text":"so a lot of wisdom never gets passed on,"},{"time":11150,"text":"though we do share the same public spaces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14102,"text":"So over the past few years,\nI've tried ways to share more"},{"time":16887,"text":"with my neighbors in public space,"},{"time":19227,"text":"using simple tools like\nstickers, stencils and chalk."},{"time":22798,"text":"And these projects came\nfrom questions I had, like:"},{"time":26194,"text":"How much are my neighbors\npaying for their apartments?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28909,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30123,"text":"How can we lend and borrow more things,"},{"time":32401,"text":"without knocking on each\nother's doors at a bad time?"},{"time":36718,"text":"How can we share more memories\nof our abandoned buildings,"},{"time":40795,"text":"and gain a better understanding\nof our landscape?"},{"time":44551,"text":"How can we share more of our hopes\nfor our vacant storefronts,"},{"time":48893,"text":"so our communities can reflect\nour needs and dreams today?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54774,"text":"Now, I live in New Orleans,"},{"time":56729,"text":"and I am in love with New Orleans."},{"time":59400,"text":"My soul is always soothed\nby the giant live oak trees,"},{"time":63932,"text":"shading lovers, drunks and dreamers\nfor hundreds of years,"},{"time":68328,"text":"and I trust a city that always\nmakes way for music."},{"time":71614,"text":"I feel like every time someone sneezes,"},{"time":74056,"text":"New Orleans has a parade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75319,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76628,"text":"The city has some of the most\nbeautiful architecture in the world,"},{"time":80168,"text":"but it also has one of the highest amounts\nof abandoned properties in America."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84802,"text":"I live near this house,"},{"time":86254,"text":"and I thought about how I could\nmake it a nicer space for my neighborhood,"},{"time":90119,"text":"and I also thought about something\nthat changed my life forever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96306,"text":"In 2009, I lost someone I loved very much."},{"time":100670,"text":"Her name was Joan,\nand she was a mother to me."},{"time":104574,"text":"And her death was sudden and unexpected."},{"time":111164,"text":"And I thought about death a lot."},{"time":117561,"text":"And ... this made me feel deep\ngratitude for the time I've had."},{"time":124242,"text":"And ... brought clarity to the things\nthat are meaningful to my life now."},{"time":134663,"text":"But I struggle to maintain\nthis perspective in my daily life."},{"time":139464,"text":"I feel like it's easy to get\ncaught up in the day-to-day,"},{"time":142297,"text":"and forget what really matters to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144980,"text":"So with help from old and new friends,"},{"time":147134,"text":"I turned the side of this abandoned\nhouse into a giant chalkboard,"},{"time":151012,"text":"and stenciled it with\na fill-in-the-blank sentence:"},{"time":153943,"text":"\"Before I die, I want to ...\""},{"time":158463,"text":"So anyone walking by\ncan pick up a piece of chalk,"},{"time":161566,"text":"reflect on their life,"},{"time":162988,"text":"and share their personal\naspirations in public space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167486,"text":"I didn't know what to expect\nfrom this experiment,"},{"time":170604,"text":"but by the next day,\nthe wall was entirely filled out,"},{"time":173949,"text":"and it kept growing."},{"time":175941,"text":"And I'd like to share a few things\nthat people wrote on this wall."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181944,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto be tried for piracy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":185401,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192201,"text":"\"Before I die, I want to straddle\nthe International Dateline.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":198208,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto sing for millions.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":202979,"text":"\"Before I die, I want to plant a tree.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":208727,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto live off the grid.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":213350,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto hold her one more time.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":219779,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto be someone's cavalry.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":225565,"text":"\"Before I die, I want\nto be completely myself.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":233971,"text":"So this neglected space\nbecame a constructive one,"},{"time":237970,"text":"and people's hopes and dreams\nmade me laugh out loud, tear up,"},{"time":242866,"text":"and they consoled me\nduring my own tough times."},{"time":246106,"text":"It's about knowing you're not alone;"},{"time":248544,"text":"it's about understanding our neighbors\nin new and enlightening ways;"},{"time":252250,"text":"it's about making space\nfor reflection and contemplation,"},{"time":255623,"text":"and remembering what really matters\nmost to us as we grow and change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262159,"text":"I made this last year,"},{"time":263420,"text":"and started receiving hundreds\nof messages from passionate people"},{"time":266839,"text":"who wanted to make a wall\nwith their community."},{"time":269280,"text":"So, my civic center colleagues\nand I made a tool kit,"},{"time":272480,"text":"and now walls have been made\nin countries around the world,"},{"time":275322,"text":"including Kazakhstan,"},{"time":278759,"text":"South Africa,"},{"time":281494,"text":"Australia,"},{"time":283970,"text":"Argentina, and beyond."},{"time":286429,"text":"Together, we've shown how powerful\nour public spaces can be"},{"time":289335,"text":"if we're given the opportunity\nto have a voice,"},{"time":292060,"text":"and share more with one another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297667,"text":"Two of the most valuable things we have"},{"time":299803,"text":"are time, and our relationships\nwith other people."},{"time":304262,"text":"In our age of increasing distractions,"},{"time":306810,"text":"it's more important than ever\nto find ways to maintain perspective,"},{"time":310310,"text":"and remember that life\nis brief and tender."},{"time":314268,"text":"Death is something that we're\noften discouraged to talk about,"},{"time":317332,"text":"or even think about,"},{"time":318626,"text":"but I've realized that preparing for death"},{"time":320974,"text":"is one of the most empowering\nthings you can do."},{"time":324204,"text":"Thinking about death clarifies your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329711,"text":"Our shared spaces can better\nreflect what matters to us,"},{"time":332624,"text":"as individuals and as a community,"},{"time":335937,"text":"and with more ways to share\nour hopes, fears and stories,"},{"time":339897,"text":"the people around us can not only\nhelp us make better places,"},{"time":343841,"text":"they can help us lead better lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346285,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347461,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":352058,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353238,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}